S'Easily monitor Bitcoin (BTC) price directly from your android smartphone!\xe2\x98\x86 Following exchanges are supported:- MtGox : http://mtgox.com- Canadian Virtual Exchange : http://cavirtex.com- BTC-E : http://btc-e.com- Bitstamp : http://bitstamp.net- CampBX : http://campbx.com - Bitcoin Central: https://bitcoin-central.net/- Bitfloor: https://bitfloor.com/- Bitcoin-24: https://bitcoin-24.com/\xe2\x98\x86 BitcoinCharts ticker list available for unsupported exchanges \xe2\x98\x86 Compact widget that displays the following information:\xe2\x80\xa2 Price of last trade\xe2\x80\xa2 Lowest price last 24 hours\xe2\x80\xa2 Highest price last 24 hours\xe2\x80\xa2 Volume of last 24 hours\xe2\x80\xa2 Time of last data refresh (Green for successful, Red for unsuccessful)\xe2\x80\xa2 Can replace High/Low with Bid/Ask\xe2\x80\xa2 Ability to refresh only on WiFi\xe2\x98\x86  Support for all MtGox currencies  MtGox can be displayed in any of the following currencies:- EUR - Euro- CAD - Canadian Dollar- GBP - British Pound- CHF - Swiss Francs- RUB - Russian Rubles- AUD - Australian Dollars- SEK - Swedish Krona- DKK - Danish Krona- HKD - Hong Kong Dollars- PLN - Polish Zloty- CNY - Chinese Yuan- SGD - Singapore Dollars- THB - Thai Baht- NZD - New Zealand Dollars- JPY - Japanese Yen\xe2\x98\x86 Price Alarm Notifications. Always be the first to know when a drastic change in the Bitcoin market occurs using notifications on your phone. Can also enable notifications to have sound and vibrate to make sure you don\'t miss your opportunities. *NEW* "Hardcore Mode" Overrides silent/vibration mode and keeps ringing loudly until shut of manually.\xe2\x98\x86 Plot price during the last week in a clean and simple graph. Now scroll and pinch-to-zoom enabled\xe2\x98\x86 Customizable widget  refresh intervals and power saving mode to reduce battery usage\xe2\x98\x86 Get your miners Bitcoin Mining statistics:DeepBitBitMinterSlushEclipseMC50BTC\xe2\x98\x86 In-app Orderbook with with liquidity highlighting *Can now be customized*      \xe2\x80\xa2 Less than 10 BTC will appear RED      \xe2\x80\xa2 Between 10 and 50  BTC will appear YELLOW      \xe2\x80\xa2 Over 50 BTC will appear GREEN\xe2\x98\x86 Charts from multiple sources and current orderbook view-able within the applicationHere is a sneak peak at upcoming features I will be working on:Short term:- Mining Widget (with alarm to notify that that miner is down)- Initial LTC and NMC support from BTC-E (Widget only for now)- Open Exchange Rates Widget- LibertyBit exchange supportLong term:- Exchange Account information- In-App Trading support- Perhaps a UI re-haul?If you have any features you would like that are not listed here or would like to help implement some of these features please feel free to email me.Please support development of this app by donating to 1yjDmiukhB2i1XyVw5t7hpAK4WXo32d54Ad-free version of Bitcoinium: play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.veken0m.bitcoinium*Bitcoinium Prime will get new updates and features sooner than the Ad-supported version.*Recent changes:1.5.3a (proper release)- Widget Theme Customization!- Improved MtGox loading times- Add Price Alarm settings menu button- Tweaked widget layout for triple digit prices- Added shorter widget refresh intervals- Replace progress dialogs with "spinners"- Tapping Price Alarm notification now opens price alarm settings- Removed "classic" graphing library- Remove Bitfloor (shut down)- Many other fixes1.5.3 (rushed release)- MtGox API fix'
